Hi, I've applied to be a reader in the summer and in the fall 2015. Everytime I update something in the summer application (i.e. the course interest list) and resubmit, and check the fall application the same updates appear. I'm not sure if I should be worried about this. Does this mean when I resubmit for summer after updating some info, it also automatically resubmits for fall, because all the information is also changed on the fall application. 

Is there a way we can see the official application that is currently submitted? I am a bit confused and worried the two applications keep updating each other when I make a change on one of them. :(
